# Production Environment Variables Template
# Copy these to Vercel Environment Variables Dashboard

# ==================================================================================
# WALLETCONNECT CLOUD PROJECT ID (REQUIRED!)
# ==================================================================================
# Get your production Project ID from: https://cloud.reown.com
# NEVER use the default development Project ID in production!
NEXT_PUBLIC_WALLET_CONNECT_PROJECT_ID=your-production-project-id-here

# ==================================================================================
# ALCHEMY API KEY (OPTIONAL BUT RECOMMENDED)
# ==================================================================================
# Get your API key from: https://dashboard.alchemyapi.io
# Provides better RPC reliability and rate limits for Base Sepolia
NEXT_PUBLIC_ALCHEMY_API_KEY=your-alchemy-api-key-here

# ==================================================================================
# DEPLOYMENT INSTRUCTIONS
# ==================================================================================
#
# 1. Create WalletConnect Cloud Project:
#    - Visit: https://cloud.reown.com
#    - Create new project
#    - Add your Vercel deployment URLs to allowed origins
#
# 2. Set Environment Variables in Vercel:
#    - Go to: Project Settings > Environment Variables
#    - Add NEXT_PUBLIC_WALLET_CONNECT_PROJECT_ID
#    - Add NEXT_PUBLIC_ALCHEMY_API_KEY (optional)
#    - Apply to: Production, Preview, and Development environments
#
# 3. Redeploy your application after setting environment variables
#
# ==================================================================================
